    "description": "欢迎来到真知之岛：一款精彩的共享世界益智游戏，环境设定在满是古代奇观与自然美景的奇幻王国之中。这里有待解决的谜题、待揭开的秘密和待发现的美景。这宁静的浮岛群是放松身心的绝佳之地，按你自己的节奏，踏上这段谜题冒险之旅吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/365951da5c901194d2716a26583642c0.webp?t=1730308751\" width=616 height=56 /></span><br>24种谜题类型，超过1万道谜题等你发现和解决，每个角落都会见证你灵感乍现的尤里卡时刻。从机关到逻辑推理、环境挑战等等，所有谜题都由优秀团队精心设计，多元化的难度设定对新手玩家友好，对老玩家来说也妙趣横生。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/12c9cf19e7c2a5ef3f926807f061fb4b.poster.avif?t=1730308751\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/12c9cf19e7c2a5ef3f926807f061fb4b.webm?t=1730308751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/7745bf80554056cdfe7c74d3c1c5a560.webp?t=1730308751\" width=616 height=56 /></span><br>自由探索主岛屿广阔的开放世界，大部分谜题和秘密都能在那里找到答案。5个生物群落景色与建筑各异，在其中悠然漫步，或在上空展翅翱翔。腾云驾雾，上天入地，发现游戏的新高度。完成20多块飞地上精心设计的谜题挑战，还可解锁全新区域。身之所往，心之所向。这里唯一的路，就是你脚下的这一条。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/a06d53b934c66de627568405a75b9a48.poster.avif?t=1730308751\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/a06d53b934c66de627568405a75b9a48.webm?t=1730308751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/f91b1ec2417c457be0ece85579decdb8.webp?t=1730308751\" width=616 height=56 /></span><br>在充满新发现的解谜旅程中，扮演探索者角色。踏上探索之路，好奇心引导你穿越令人叹为观止的开放世界，答案总是在眼前。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/482f06382d4319148298e8c08bdee3d4.poster.avif?t=1730308751\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/482f06382d4319148298e8c08bdee3d4.webm?t=1730308751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/a9c1274f5dc2f0576d4e89a1e0c6ab78.webp?t=1730308751\" width=616 height=56 /></span><br>定制角色，运筹帷幄，提高等级，赚取火花，解锁全新技能，完成每日任务。与全球玩家实时互动，可以求助他人，也可以自力更生解决难题。真知之岛上，持续更新的谜题和源源不断的精彩在等着你。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/96ccca64cc7ef734c34f3738797e766b.poster.avif?t=1730308751\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071500/extras/96ccca64cc7ef734c34f3738797e766b.webm?t=1730308751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>访问此游戏内容可能会受到年龄限制。",
